---
layout: "blog.njk"
title: "Blog Francelino Turismo"
description: "Acompanhe as melhores dicas de viagem, compras no Paraguai e roteiros para a Tríplice Fronteira."
---

<div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 60px;">
    <h2 style="color: #5CB8FF; font-size: 2.5rem;">Nossas Dicas e Roteiros</h2>
    <p style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); font-size: 1.1rem; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto;">Fique por dentro das atualizações mais recentes para economizar nas compras e aproveitar a viagem!</p>
</div>

<div class="blog-grid" style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr)); gap: 30px; text-align: left;">
  {% for post in collections.blog | reverse %}
    <a href="{{ post.url }}" style="background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03); border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); border-radius: 20px; overflow: hidden; display: flex; flex-direction: column; text-decoration: none; color: white; transition: all 0.3s ease; box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);">
      
      <div style="padding: 30px; flex: 1; display: flex; flex-direction: column;">
          <h3 style="color: #FF5C00; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 1.4rem; line-height: 1.3;">{{ post.data.title }}</h3>
          <p style="font-size: 0.95rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 25px; flex: 1;">
            {{ post.data.description }}
          </p>
          <div style="margin-top: auto;">
              <span style="display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; color: #5CB8FF; font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.9rem;">
                  Ler Artigo Completo <span>&rarr;</span>
              </span>
          </div>
      </div>
    </a>
  {% else %}
    <div style="grid-column: 1 / -1; text-align: center; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05); padding: 50px; border-radius: 20px;">
        <h3 style="color: #fff; margin-bottom: 10px;">Nenhum artigo publicado ainda.</h3>
        <p style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);">Acesse o painel do seu site e escreva sua primeira matéria!</p>
    </div>
  {% endfor %}
</div>
